# Native build trees and generated installs
# (list the suffixed variants EXPLICITLY rather than a broad build*/ install*/ glob —
#  the bare build/ install/ patterns missed build_miniforge/ install_miniforge/, so
#  18+15 generated artifacts were tracked by accident; a broad *.glob risks catching
#  unrelated source dirs like installer/ or buildtools/.)
**/build/
**/build_miniforge/
**/cmake-build-*/
**/CMakeFiles/
**/CMakeCache.txt
**/install/
**/install_miniforge/

# Large local archives/artifacts
*.tar.gz
*.tgz
*.zip
*.pptx

# Generated analysis outputs
graphify-out/
wiki/

# Self-contained RTTOV execution bundle (binaries + coef/hydrotable; ~12 MB).
# Rebuild from AD-RTTOV with tools/build_rttov_runtime.sh (see rttov_runtime/README.md).
rttov_runtime/

# Local editor/project config
**/.obsidian/
xclaudex.toml
